x4freetext: The targets were obtained by vacuum evaporation of
metallic beryllium of B203 (95% 10B enriched)
on polyvinilformal backings. The measurements of the
target thickness were performed only for the target
used to obtain the data at Ed=2 MeV and theta=90 degr.
and were 0.34 mu-m for the 9Be and 0.09 mu-m for the
B2O3 target.
